Invocation Name: we buy homes
des:
The “We Buy Homes” service is provided by real estate investors, who are individual investors that buy houses, or companies that buy houses from people who must have a house sold quickly or with a high level of urgency. 

The Skill can help you understand what how does "We Buy Homes" service works and can guide you on how to sell your property fast.
